Package adrenaline.server.controller

Class Lobby

  • java.lang.Object
    • adrenaline.server.controller.Lobby
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LobbyAPI, java.lang.Runnable, java.rmi.Remote
    public class Lobby
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable, LobbyAPI
    The lobby class implements Runnable, LobbyAPI,To control model and return the operation result to high level. Every game have a lobby,and entry the game lift can exist a lot of lobby,so a lot of game in parallel.
